WITH "t1" AS (SELECT "a"."student_id","a"."student_name","b"."subject_name" FROM ("Students" AS "a") JOIN "Subjects" AS "b"), "t2" AS (SELECT "student_id","subject_name",COUNT("subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM "Examinations" GROUP BY "student_id","subject_name") SELECT "t1"."student_id","t1"."student_name","t1"."subject_name",COALESCE("t2"."attended_exams", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM "t1" LEFT JOIN "t2" ON "t1"."student_id"="t2"."student_id" AND "t1"."subject_name"="t2"."subject_name" GROUP BY "t1"."student_id","t1"."subject_name","t1"."student_name" ORDER BY "t1"."student_id","t1"."subject_name"

SELECT "ST"."student_id","ST"."student_name","SU"."subject_name",COUNT("E"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "ST" JOIN "subjects" AS "SU") LEFT JOIN "examinations" AS "E" ON "ST"."student_id"="E"."student_id" AND "SU"."subject_name"="E"."subject_name" GROUP BY "ST"."student_id","SU"."subject_name" ORDER BY "ST"."student_id","SU"."subject_name"

WITH "student_subjects" AS (SELECT * FROM "Students" JOIN "Subjects") SELECT "temp"."student_id","temp"."student_name","temp"."subject_name","temp"."attended_exams" FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "student_subjects"."subject_name",COUNT("Examinations"."subject_name") OVER (PARTITION BY "Examinations"."subject_name", "Examinations"."student_id") AS "attended_exams","student_subjects"."student_id","student_subjects"."student_name" FROM "Examinations" RIGHT JOIN "student_subjects" ON "student_subjects"."student_id"="Examinations"."student_id" AND "student_subjects"."subject_name"="Examinations"."subject_name") AS "temp" ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

SELECT "a"."student_id","student_name","b"."subject_name",COALESCE("ct", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM ("students" AS "a" JOIN "subjects" AS "b") LEFT JOIN (SELECT "student_id","subject_name",COUNT(1) AS "ct" FROM "examinations" GROUP BY "student_id","subject_name") AS "e" ON "a"."student_id"="e"."student_id" AND "b"."subject_name"="e"."subject_name" ORDER BY "a"."student_id","b"."subject_name"

SELECT "s"."student_id","student_name","Subjects"."subject_name",COALESCE("attended_exams", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "s" JOIN "Subjects") LEFT JOIN (SELECT *,COUNT(1) AS "attended_exams" FROM "Examinations" GROUP BY 1,2) AS "temp" ON "Subjects"."subject_name"="temp"."subject_name" AND "s"."student_id"="temp"."student_id" ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "e"."student_id","s"."student_name","e"."subject_name",COUNT("e"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM "Examinations" AS "e" LEFT JOIN "Students" AS "s" ON "e"."student_id"="s"."student_id" GROUP BY "e"."student_id","e"."subject_name"), "cte2" AS (SELECT * FROM "Students" AS "s1" JOIN "Subjects" AS "s2") SELECT "cte2".*,COALESCE("cte"."attended_exams", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM "cte2" LEFT JOIN "cte" ON "cte2"."student_id"="cte"."student_id" AND "cte2"."subject_name"="cte"."subject_name" ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

WITH "initital" AS (SELECT "st"."student_id","st"."student_name","su"."subject_name" FROM "students" AS "st" JOIN "subjects" AS "su") SELECT "i"."student_id","i"."student_name","i"."subject_name",COALESCE("agg"."x", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM "initital" AS "i" LEFT JOIN (SELECT "student_id","subject_name",COUNT(1) AS "x" FROM "examinations" GROUP BY 1,2) AS "AGG" ON "i"."student_id"="agg"."student_id" AND "i"."subject_name"="agg"."subject_name" ORDER BY 1,3

SELECT "student_id","student_name","subject_name",COUNT("cnt") AS "attended_exams" FROM (SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name","e"."subject_name" AS "cnt" FROM ("Students" AS "s" JOIN "Subjects" AS "sub") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "e" ON "s"."student_id"="e"."student_id" AND "sub"."subject_name"="e"."subject_name") AS "tmp" GROUP BY "student_id","subject_name" ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

SELECT "ss".*,COUNT("e"."student_id") AS "attended_exams" FROM (SELECT "st"."student_id","st"."student_name","s"."subject_name" FROM ("subjects" AS "s") JOIN "students" AS "st") AS "ss" LEFT JOIN "examinations" AS "e" ON "ss"."student_id"="e"."student_id" AND "ss"."subject_name"="e"."subject_name" GROUP BY "student_id","student_name","subject_name" ORDER BY 1,3

SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name",COUNT("e"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "s" JOIN "Subjects" AS "sub") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "e" ON "s"."student_id"="e"."student_id" AND "sub"."subject_name"="e"."subject_name" GROUP BY "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name" ORDER BY "s"."student_id"

WITH "cte_join" AS (SELECT "stdnt"."student_id","student_name","s"."subject_name",COUNT("e"."student_id") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "stdnt" JOIN "Subjects" AS "s") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "e" ON "stdnt"."student_id"="e"."student_id" AND "s"."subject_name"="e"."subject_name" GROUP BY 1,2,3 ORDER BY 1,3) SELECT * FROM "cte_join"

SELECT "student"."student_id","student"."student_name","subject"."subject_name",COUNT("exam"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "student" JOIN "Subjects" AS "subject") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "exam" ON "student"."student_id"="exam"."student_id" AND "subject"."subject_name"="exam"."subject_name" GROUP BY "student"."student_id","subject"."subject_name" ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

SELECT "Students"."student_id","Students"."student_name","Subjects"."subject_name",COUNT("Examinations"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" JOIN "Subjects") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" ON "Examinations"."student_id"="Students"."student_id" AND "Examinations"."subject_name"="Subjects"."subject_name" GROUP BY "Students"."student_id","Subjects"."subject_name" ORDER BY "Students"."student_id","Subjects"."subject_name"

WITH "all_student_subjects" AS (SELECT * FROM "students" AS "s" JOIN "subjects" AS "su") SELECT "a"."student_id","a"."student_name","a"."subject_name",COALESCE("e"."attended_exams", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM "all_student_subjects" AS "a" LEFT JOIN (SELECT "student_id","subject_name",COUNT(1) AS "attended_exams" FROM "examinations" GROUP BY "student_id","subject_name") AS "e" ON "e"."student_id"="a"."student_id" AND "e"."subject_name"="a"."subject_name" ORDER BY 1,3

SELECT "c"."student_id","c"."student_name","c"."subject_name",COUNT("e"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM (SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name" FROM ("Students" AS "s") JOIN "Subjects" AS "sub") AS "c" LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "e" ON "e"."student_id"="c"."student_id" AND "c"."subject_name"="e"."subject_name" GROUP BY "c"."student_id","c"."student_name","c"."subject_name" ORDER BY "c"."student_id"

SELECT "t"."student_id","student_name","t"."subject_name",COALESCE(COUNT("et"."subject_name"), 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM (SELECT "st"."student_id","student_name","s"."subject_name" FROM ("Students" AS "st") JOIN "subjects" AS "s") AS "t" LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "et" ON "t"."student_id"="et"."student_id" AND "t"."subject_name"="et"."subject_name" GROUP BY "student_id","subject_name" ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

SELECT "A"."student_id","A"."student_name","B"."subject_name",(SELECT COUNT(1) FROM "Examinations" AS "C" WHERE "A"."student_id"="C"."student_id" AND "B"."subject_name"="C"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM "Students" AS "A" JOIN "Subjects" AS "B" ORDER BY "A"."student_id","B"."subject_name"

SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name",COUNT("e"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "s" JOIN "Subjects" AS "sub") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "e" USING ("student_id","subject_name") GROUP BY "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name" ORDER BY "s"."student_id"

SELECT "stu"."student_id","stu"."student_name","sub"."subject_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "exam"."student_id"="stu"."student_id" AND "exam"."subject_name"="sub"."subject_name" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "stu" JOIN "Subjects" AS "sub") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "exam" ON "exam"."student_id"="stu"."student_id" AND "exam"."subject_name"="sub"."subject_name" GROUP BY 1,2,3 ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT "s".*,"sub".*,COALESCE("sub1"."ct", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM ("students" AS "s" JOIN "Subjects" AS "sub") LEFT JOIN (SELECT "student_id","subject_name",COUNT(1) AS "ct" FROM "Examinations" GROUP BY 1,2 ORDER BY 1) AS "sub1" USING ("student_id","subject_name") ORDER BY "s"."student_id","subject_name"

SELECT "student"."student_id","student"."student_name","subject"."subject_name",COUNT("exam"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "student" JOIN "Subjects" AS "subject") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "exam" ON "student"."student_id"="exam"."student_id" AND "subject"."subject_name"="exam"."subject_name" GROUP BY "student"."student_id","subject"."subject_name" ORDER BY "student_id","subject"."subject_name"

WITH "t1" AS (SELECT "stu"."student_id","Student_name","sub"."subject_name" FROM "Students" AS "stu" JOIN "Subjects" AS "sub"), "t2" AS (SELECT "t1"."student_id","t1"."student_name","t1"."subject_name","e"."subject_name" AS "taken_subject" FROM "t1" LEFT JOIN "examinations" AS "e" ON "t1"."student_id"="e"."student_id" AND "t1"."subject_name"="e"."subject_name") SELECT "t2"."student_id","t2"."student_name","t2"."subject_name",COUNT("t2"."taken_subject") AS "attended_exams" FROM "t2" GROUP BY "subject_name","student_name","student_id" ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","su"."subject_name",COALESCE("t"."attended_exams", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "s" JOIN "Subjects" AS "su") LEFT JOIN (SELECT *,COUNT("subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM "Examinations" GROUP BY "student_id","subject_name") AS "t" ON "s"."student_id"="t"."student_id" AND "su"."subject_name"="t"."subject_name" ORDER BY 1,3

SELECT "z1"."student_id","z1"."student_name","z3"."subject_name",(COUNT("z2"."subject_name")) AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "z1" JOIN "Subjects" AS "z3") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "z2" ON "z1"."student_id"="z2"."student_id" AND "z2"."subject_name"="z3"."subject_name" GROUP BY 1,2,3 ORDER BY 1,3

SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","s"."subject_name",SUM(CASE WHEN "e"."subject_name" IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "attended_exams" FROM (SELECT "student_id","student_name","subject_name" FROM ("Students") JOIN "Subjects") AS "s" LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "e" ON "s"."student_id"="e"."student_id" AND "s"."subject_name"="e"."subject_name" GROUP BY 2,3 ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name",COUNT("ex"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("students" AS "s" JOIN "subjects" AS "sub") LEFT JOIN "examinations" AS "ex" USING ("student_id","subject_name") GROUP BY "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name" ORDER BY "s"."student_id","s"."student_name"

SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","s2"."subject_name",COUNT("e"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "s" JOIN "Subjects" AS "s2") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "e" ON "e"."student_id"="s"."student_id" AND "e"."subject_name"="s2"."subject_name" GROUP BY 1,2,3 ORDER BY 1,2

SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","b"."subject_name",COUNT("e"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "s" JOIN "Subjects" AS "b") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "e" ON "b"."subject_name"="e"."subject_name" AND "s"."student_id"="e"."student_id" GROUP BY 1,3 ORDER BY 1,3

SELECT "student"."student_id","student"."student_name","subject"."subject_name",COUNT("exam"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "student" JOIN "Subjects" AS "subject") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "exam" ON "student"."student_id"="exam"."student_id" AND "subject"."subject_name"="exam"."subject_name" GROUP BY "student"."student_id","subject"."subject_name" ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name",COUNT("ex"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("students" AS "s" JOIN "subjects" AS "sub") LEFT JOIN "examinations" AS "ex" USING ("student_id","subject_name") GROUP BY "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name" ORDER BY "s"."student_id","s"."student_name"

WITH "table1" AS (SELECT DISTINCT "Students"."student_id","Students"."student_name","Subjects"."subject_name" FROM "Students" JOIN "Subjects"), "table2" AS (SELECT "student_id","subject_name",COUNT("subject_name") AS "cnt" FROM "Examinations" GROUP BY "student_id","subject_name") SELECT "table1"."student_id","table1"."student_name","table1"."subject_name",CASE WHEN "table2"."cnt" IS NULL=1 THEN 0 ELSE "table2"."cnt" END AS "attended_exams" FROM "table1" LEFT JOIN "table2" ON "table1"."student_id"="table2"."student_id" AND "table1"."subject_name"="table2"."subject_name" ORDER BY "table1"."student_id","table1"."subject_name"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "student_id","subject_name",COUNT(1) AS "CNT" FROM "examinations" GROUP BY "student_id","subject_name") SELECT "a"."student_id","student_name","b"."subject_name",COALESCE("c"."cnt", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM ("students" AS "a" JOIN "subjects" AS "b") LEFT JOIN "cte" AS "c" ON "a"."student_id"="c"."student_id" AND "c"."subject_name"="b"."subject_name" ORDER BY "a"."student_id","b"."subject_name"

SELECT "s"."student_id","student_name","sub"."subject_name",COUNT("e"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "s" JOIN "Subjects" AS "sub") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "e" ON ("s"."student_id"="e"."student_id" AND "e"."subject_name"="sub"."subject_name") GROUP BY "s"."student_id","sub"."subject_name" ORDER BY "s"."student_id","sub"."subject_name"

SELECT "a"."student_id","student_name","b"."subject_name",COALESCE(COUNT("c"."subject_name"), 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM ("students" AS "a" JOIN "subjects" AS "b") LEFT JOIN "examinations" AS "c" ON "a"."student_id"="c"."student_id" AND "b"."subject_name"="c"."subject_name" GROUP BY "a"."student_id","b"."subject_name" ORDER BY "a"."student_id","b"."subject_name"

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "student_id","subject_name",COUNT(1) AS "exams" FROM "examinations" GROUP BY 1,2) SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","j"."subject_name",COALESCE("exams", 0) AS "attended_exams" FROM ("students" AS "s" JOIN "subjects" AS "j") LEFT JOIN "cte" AS "c" ON "s"."student_id"="c"."student_id" AND "j"."subject_name"="c"."subject_name" ORDER BY 1,3

SELECT "student"."student_id","student"."student_name","subject"."subject_name",COUNT("exam"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" AS "student" JOIN "Subjects" AS "subject") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" AS "exam" ON "student"."student_id"="exam"."student_id" AND "subject"."subject_name"="exam"."subject_name" GROUP BY "student"."student_id","subject"."subject_name" ORDER BY "student_id","subject_name"

SELECT "Students".*,"Subjects".*,COUNT("Examinations"."student_id") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("Students" JOIN "Subjects") LEFT JOIN "Examinations" USING ("student_id","subject_name") GROUP BY "student_id","subject_name" ORDER BY "student_id","student_name","subject_name"

SELECT "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name",COUNT("ex"."subject_name") AS "attended_exams" FROM ("students" AS "s" JOIN "subjects" AS "sub") LEFT JOIN "examinations" AS "ex" USING ("student_id","subject_name") GROUP BY "s"."student_id","s"."student_name","sub"."subject_name" ORDER BY "s"."student_id","s"."student_name"
